fehd.ADR_EN: SHOP NO. 1, G/F., JADE CENTRE, 98 WELLINGTON STREET, CENTRAL, HONG KONG
fehd.ADR_TC: 香港中環威靈頓街98號翡翠中心地下1號鋪

result.adr_address: 69 Wellington St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Dumpling Yuan

reviews.text: Simple and delicious pan fried dumplings. Nothing to complain about. If you want some authentic dumplings go here.  Friendly service too.

Amazing dumpling spot. we first had dumplings here at 10pm after some drinks but then we went everyday for breakfast!!! the owner is 72 and his wife knows how to make traditional tasty dumplings. Excellent value- even better with a beer- must try!!

It was situated in a very convenient spot in Central. The dumplings we're not lazy at all but yet they were not particularly delicious. so anybody who want to taste truly yummy dumplings please go to the Wan chai shop which has a similar name ( 餃子源； while this is 餃子園，tricky uh?) but belong to a different groups.

Simple but homely, fresh and healthy menu. Friendly staff and management. The place is cleaner than it looks from the outside. Menu has English translation and (some) photos. Bit more expensive that other similar places but definitely worth it - especially if you are not local!
Great food a real local experience
